《'''我们的天父'''》（{{lang-sw|'''Baba Yetu'''}}）是2005年的电子游戏[[文明IV|文明IV]]的[[主题曲|主题曲]]。它由[[田志仁|田志仁]]作曲，Ron Ragin和{{tsl|en|Stanford Talisman}}演唱。<ref>{{cite web|title=Looking Back... Civilization IV |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/142558/interviews/looking-back-civilization-iv/?page=2 |publisher=CVG |accessdate=2012-12-31 |date=2006-07-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808054803/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/142558/interviews/looking-back-civilization-iv/?page=2 |archivedate=2014-08-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Nichols|first=Max|title=Video Games Live|url=http://www.n-sider.com/contentview.php?contentid=427|accessdate=2012-07-13|newspaper=N-Sider|date=2007-09-01|archive-date=2014-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809230139/http://www.n-sider.com/contentview.php?contentid=427|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Talisman featured on Civilization 4 |url=http://www.stanfordtalisman.com/html/oldnews2.html |accessdate=2014-12-21 |date=2005-03-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808043958/http://www.stanfordtalisman.com/html/oldnews2.html |archivedate=2014-08-08 }}</ref> 这首歌曲亦被收录于田志仁的专辑《{{tsl|en|Calling All Dawns}}》，专辑中的歌曲由[[索韦托福音合唱团|索韦托福音合唱团]]演唱。

2007年，《我们的天父》即由{{tsl|en|Alfred Music}}发行，<ref>{{cite web|title=Baba Yetu|url=http://www.alfred-music.com/product_info.php?products_id=5876|publisher=Alfred Music|accessdate=2013-01-03|archive-date=2019-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191225051723/https://www.alfred-music.com/product_info.php?products_id=5876|dead-url=no}}</ref>2011年，田志仁又重新编排了这首歌曲。<ref>{{cite web|title=Baba Yetu - SATB|url=http://www.alfred-music.com/product_info.php?products_id=8660|publisher=Alfred Music|accessdate=2012-07-13|archive-date=2011-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111004154355/http://www.alfred-music.com/product_info.php?products_id=8660|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==奖项==
《Baba Yetu》被提名为[[第53届格莱美奖|第53届格莱美奖]]的{{tsl|en|Grammy Award for Best Arrangement, Instrumental and Vocals|格莱美最佳器乐编排及伴奏奖|最佳器乐编排及伴奏奖}}，使其成为第一首被提名格莱美奖的游戏主题曲。<ref>{{cite news|last=Langshaw|first=Mark|title='Civ IV' theme nominated for Grammy|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/news/a291495/civ-iv-theme-nominated-for-grammy.html|accessdate=2012-12-31|newspaper=Digital Spy|date=2010-12-05|archive-date=2014-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102220353/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/news/a291495/civ-iv-theme-nominated-for-grammy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2011年2月13日，《Baba Yetu》获正式夺得该奖项，让其成为第一首获格莱美奖的游戏歌曲。<ref>{{cite news|last=Senior|first=Tom|title=Civilization 4 wins grammy for Baba Yetu six years after release|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/02/14/civilization-4-wins-grammy-award/|accessdate=2012-12-31|newspaper=PC Gamer|date=2011-02-14|archive-date=2015-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150411004010/http://www.pcgamer.com/civilization-4-wins-grammy-award/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在第10届年度独立音乐奖（Independent Music Awards）上，它获得了Song Used in Film/TV/Multimedia和World Beat Song奖项。<ref name=IMA>{{cite web|url=http://www.independentmusicawards.com/ima/artist/christopher-tin|title=Christopher Tin|publisher=The Independent Music Awards|accessdate=2012-12-31|archive-date=2012-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120821135541/http://www.independentmusicawards.com/ima/artist/christopher-tin|dead-url=no}}</ref>并且，在2006年的Game Audio Network Guild奖上获得两项大奖。<ref name=Resume>{{cite web|title=Christopher Tin: Composer |url=http://www.tinworksmusic.com/ChristopherTin_Composer_Resume_10-2012.pdf |publisher=Tin Works |accessdate=2012-12-31 |date=2012-10-10 }}{{dead link|date=October 2016 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

==重要表演==
《Baba Yetu》经常在重要场合和事件中演奏，比如[[卡内基大厅|卡内基大厅]]、[[林肯表演艺术中心|林肯表演艺术中心]]、[[华特·迪士尼音乐厅|华特·迪士尼音乐厅]]、[[迪拜喷泉|迪拜喷泉]]等。<ref>{{cite AV media |title=Viva Vox Choir (Belgrade) - New Year's Concert of the 67th Session of the General Assembly |url=http://webtv.un.org/watch/viva-vox-choir-belgrade-new-years-concert-of-the-67th-session-of-the-general-assembly/2094291812001/ |accessdate=2013-01-15 |date=2013-01-14 |time=25:29 |publisher=UN Web TV |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111212254/http://webtv.un.org/watch/viva-vox-choir-belgrade-new-years-concert-of-the-67th-session-of-the-general-assembly/2094291812001/#full-text }}</ref>它也经常由名演唱团演唱，比如[[皇家爱乐乐团|皇家爱乐乐团]]、<ref name="Cadogan">{{cite news|url=http://www.cadoganhall.com/event/the-music-of-christopher-tin-160719/|title=The Music of Christopher Tin at Cadogan Hal|date=2016-07-19|newspaper=Cadogan Hall|accessdate=2017-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170831131141/http://www.cadoganhall.com/event/the-music-of-christopher-tin-160719/|archive-date=2017-08-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[国家交响乐团_(美国)|国家交响乐团]]、<ref name="VGLKennedyCenter">{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/07/01/AR2007070101112.html|title=It's All in the Playing at NSO's 'Video Games Live'|date=2007-07-02|newspaper=Washington Post|accessdate=2017-08-31|archive-date=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108181208/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/07/01/AR2007070101112.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{tsl|en|US Navy Band|美国海军军乐团}}。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://nairobinews.nation.co.ke/chillax/us-navy-band-performs-baba-yetu-in-kiswahili-and-its-astonishing/|title=US Navy Band Performs ‘Baba Yetu’ in Swahili and it's Astonishing|date=2016-01-20|newspaper=Nairobi News|accessdate=2017-08-31|archive-date=2019-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210011709/https://nairobinews.nation.co.ke/chillax/us-navy-band-performs-baba-yetu-in-kiswahili-and-its-astonishing|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==反响==

"Baba Yetu"获得了包括[[IGN|IGN]]、[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]和[[GameShark|GameShark]]在内的媒体的广泛好评。<ref>{{cite web|last=Tin |first=Christopher |title=Press |url=http://www.christophertin.com/press.html |accessdate=2012-12-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116092938/http://www.christophertin.com/press.html |archivedate=2013-01-16 }}</ref>

==歌词==
"Baba Yetu"的歌词来自于[[斯瓦希里语|斯瓦希里语]]的[[主祷文|主祷文]]。<ref name=Tin>{{cite web|title=Calling All Dawns Digital Booklet|url=http://www.christophertin.com/assets/downloads/CallingAllDawns_DigitalBooklet.pdf.zip|publisher=Christopher Tin|year=2009|accessdate=2014-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221093418/https://www.christophertin.com/assets/downloads/CallingAllDawns_DigitalBooklet.pdf.zip|archive-date=2016-12-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

